DESCRIPTION

  File::Find::Rule::XPath - rule to match on XPath expressions

  This module extends File::Find::Rule to provide the ability to locate
  XML files which match a given XPath expression.

PREREQUISITES

  Requires either XML::LibXML or XML::XPath


BUILDING/INSTALLING

  Once the archive is unpacked, use these commands:

      perl Makefile.PL
      make
      make test
      make install


RELEASE HISTORY

  Version 0.03 fixes an incompatibility with recent versions of File::Spec


